###

Moodle Migration from one server to another

###

- Deny access from all users by enabling Maintenance Mode
- Backup Database (mysqldump)
- Backup moodledata directory (using tar)
- Backup moodle (using tar)
- Transfer all backup files
- Install and setup all depending currencies (refer to moodlestack repository)
- Unzip the files and setup a new database for moodle
- Configure the config.php in moodle directory
- Open web 
